<item>
            <title>[LU-3296] fs/lustre/mdt/*/md_stats not showing any stats after remount</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3296</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed that the md_stats proc file was empty, although there was activity on the filesystem and exports/*/stats contained several stats and were being updated. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I unmounted and remounted the fs, no change. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I rebooted, and md_stats contained usual operation stats data. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then remounted the mdt, and md_stats stayed empty again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also,  fs/lustre/mdt/*/stats is empty, and remained empty after a reboot and remounts. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My normal procedure for creating a lustre target does do a remount after the initial registration step, so it&apos;s possible this only occurs after remounting the mdt. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
